Cosmo's Cosmic Adventure by Apogee Software

Due to this game's animation requirements, it requires an
80286 or better CPU (80386, 80486, etc.) in order to run.

This game will NOT run on XT computers, which contain the
8088 or 8086 CPU.

If you upload this game to a bulletin board, please note
this in the description, so other players don't waste their
time downloading a game they cannot play.

Thank you,
Scott Miller
